songs.title: Ishoo
songs.lyrics:
Ulfina kee dhiistee waaqarraa gad buutee
Du'a na hambisuuf ofiike naaf laatte

songs.title: Ergan Fayyee
songs.lyrics:
Ergan Fayyee nan Gammadaa
nan faarsa waaqa koof iyyee

songs.title: Innichi na baate Barruunke
songs.lyrics:
Innichi na baate barruun kee suni haa eebbifamuu*2

Ani Gooftaakoo siin godhadheeraa lubbu korratti siin moosiseera

songs.title: At Dhuguma Waaqa
songs.lyrics:
At dhuguma waaqaa *3
Egaa maal Jennaree Maqaa kee faarfannaa

songs.title: TasanBannu
songs.lyrics: Hin kufnu laafnee ofirra gad hin teenyu

songs.title: Haalleeluyyaa
songs.lyrics:
Yommuu godoon keenya jijjiguu
Du'aan biyya lafaarraa godaannu
Nuti akka warra kaanii hin gaddinuu
[Arguuf jirra abbaa keenya furii lubbuu keenyaa]*2

Yeerusaleem mandara ishee haaratti galuufan jiraa
Akka hawwetti hin hafuu garaankoo dhufee nan na fudhataa
[Haalleluuyyaa]*7

Yommuu biyya abdiikoo sana gau
Beeluuf dheebuun hin hafaa
Achitti bo'ichi hin argamuu
Yeroo hundaan gammadaa nan farfaadha
[Haalleluuyyaa]*6

[Amma asitti addunya kanarraatti         
Warran of biraa isaan dhabee 
Abdii qabaa nan argaan ammas          
Yemmuu deebisee fiduun dhaaphee]*2   

[Aniis ilaala hin hafuu
Oolan butama garasaa ] *2
[Waliin jiraanna ulfinaan
Yeroo hundaa qabbana bobaasaa]*2
